took on twice as many surgeries.

494
00:35:29,628 --> 00:35:31,790
I... I hid at the hospital.

495
00:35:31,863 --> 00:35:34,594
I was afraid that I was
going to piss off my wife.

496
00:35:34,666 --> 00:35:36,931
Sound familiar?
Upset my daughter.

497
00:35:37,669 --> 00:35:40,434
- I thought you liked being a dad.
- I did. I...

498
00:35:41,406 --> 00:35:44,137
I just didn't think I
was very good at it. I...

499
00:35:44,776 --> 00:35:46,904
It didn't come naturally to me.

500
00:35:46,978 --> 00:35:49,277
Not like... Not
like brain surgery.

501
00:35:50,949 --> 00:35:52,076
I missed a lot.

502
00:35:54,619 --> 00:35:57,748
Sometimes I think if I had
been there for the swaddling

503
00:35:57,822 --> 00:36:00,018
and for the changing
of the diapers and...

504
00:36:03,128 --> 00:36:04,528
see her first steps, you know...

505
00:36:09,968 --> 00:36:11,960
Shaun, do yourself a favor,

506
00:36:12,037 --> 00:36:15,906
and be there for as many
moments as you can.

507
00:36:31,856 --> 00:36:33,154
Taking the scenic route?

508
00:36:33,958 --> 00:36:36,723
Car needs brakes and
Uber was taking forever.

509
00:36:38,630 --> 00:36:39,928
Chess guy is super cool.

