00:39:02,507 --> 00:39:04,567
I've been mad at
you for so long...

535
00:39:08,847 --> 00:39:12,181
that I couldn't feel any
other emotion, just anger.

536
00:39:13,852 --> 00:39:14,979
Angry at you...

537
00:39:16,287 --> 00:39:19,951
angry at myself for secretly wishing
you would turn up on my doorstep

538
00:39:20,024 --> 00:39:21,287
my entire life.

539
00:39:23,595 --> 00:39:24,824
I thought I'd outgrown it.

540
00:39:32,136 --> 00:39:34,002
But when you went
into surgery today...

541
00:39:37,208 --> 00:39:39,609
I didn't feel anger, I felt...

542
00:39:42,747 --> 00:39:43,747
fear.

543
00:40:11,509 --> 00:40:12,636
You get some rest.

544
00:40:18,349 --> 00:40:19,840
When you feel better, you...

545
00:40:21,786 --> 00:40:23,220
You can take me for Rocky Road.

546
00:40:25,556 --> 00:40:27,149
It is still my favorite.

547
00:40:44,909 --> 00:40:46,036
I love you.

548
00:41:10,802 --> 00:41:13,203
- Are you ready?
- Mm-hm.

549
00:41:16,741 --> 00:41:18,266
You came.

550
00:41:19,777 --> 00:41:22,770
Hello. I'm Dr. Shaun Murphy.

551
00:41:23,648 --> 00:41:24,648
I'm the dad.

552
00:41:25,717 --> 00:41:28,050
