- Shaun.

555
00:41:33,124 --> 00:41:35,889
Her diploma is not on the
wall. I would like to know.

556
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:39,727
Just be the dad. Sit
there. Be quiet. Do nothing.

557
00:41:48,106 --> 00:41:50,132
Is that the...?

558
00:41:50,208 --> 00:41:52,939
That's the heartbeat.
Right there.

